Name: Star Expansion - Origin
Description: Collect Star Expansion - Origin, Star Expansion - Core, and Star Expansion - Structure to exchange for a Miracle Star Chest at the Development Bureau.
Description2$english: The Miracle Star Chest is a beautiful reward chest, as splendid as a starry sky. Although the contents are uncertain, it is guaranteed to contain various treasures. Many adventurers hope to get rich by opening this treasure.
